                            <comment id="12890007" author="rding" created="Mon, 19 Jul 2010 21:29:15 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Looks good. A few comments:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The new test class &lt;em&gt;test/org/apache/pig/test/utils/UPPER.java&lt;/em&gt; is missing Apache header and this results in the release audit warning.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;In the test case, the line&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
w.println(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;B = FOREACH A GENERATE UPPER(name);&quot;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;should be replaced by &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
w.println(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;B = FOREACH A GENERATE org.apache.pig.test.utils.UPPER(name);&quot;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;otherwise the builtin UDF UPPER is used and job will succeed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Also in the test case, should replace&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt;(js.getState().equals(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;FAILED&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)){
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;with &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt;(js.getState().name().equals(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;FAILED&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)){
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;to perform the string comparison.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The logging in &lt;em&gt;MapReduceLauncher&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
log.info(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;jobs&quot;&lt;/span&gt; + job.getAssignedJobID() + &quot; have failed!
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;should be written as &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
log.info(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;job &quot;&lt;/span&gt; + job.getAssignedJobID() + &quot; has failed!
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
</comment>
